AmeriSource completes $ 500 mln credit line . AmeriSource Health Corp said Thursday it had completed a new five - year , $ 500 million revolving credit facility . The facility , which replaces an existing line , increases the company ' s borrowing capacity by $ 120 million . AmeriSource said it expects to use the new facility for growth and corporate development activities . The credit agreement was completed with a bank syndicate led by NationsBank Corp . 
